com.ibm.team.repository.common.query

Interface IDataRow


  • public interface IDataRow

    Represents a row of data from a data query result. The shape of a row is described by the list of IDataFields contained within the result page. The number of fields in a row will match the number of fields in the data field list.

    Since:
    0.5
